        <content><![CDATA[<h1 class="title topictitle1">Personalizing Your NeedIt List</h1>
<p>Changes to your list screen can be easily performed by following these steps.</p>
<h2 class="title sectiontitle">Changing List Layout</h2>
<ol class="steps-ordered"><li class="li step">  Click the <span class="ph uicontrol"><em>Gear</em> </span>icon above the list.  When you hover over the icon, it will display <em>Personalize  List</em>.</li><li class="li step">  The <em>Slush Bucket</em> will appear.  Select any fields from the <span class="ph uicontrol">Active</span> section and click the right arrow ( &gt; ) to move the field into the <span class="ph uicontrol">Selected</span> window.</li><li class="li step">  To remove a field,  selet the field you want to remove and use the left arrow ( &lt; ) to move it to the <span class="ph uicontrol">Active</span> section.</li><li class="li step">Click <em>OK</em> to save your changes.</li></ol>
<h2 class="title sectiontitle">Add Filter Conditions</h2>
<ol class="steps-ordered"><li class="li step">  Select the <em><span class="ph uicontrol">funnel</span></em> icon to add or remove conditions to further limit search results.</li><li class="li step">  Select <em>AND, OR, </em>or <em>Add Sort.</em></li><li class="li step">  Choose a field, add an operator, and enter a value.</li><li class="li step">Click <em>RUN<span class="ph uicontrol">,</span></em> to execute your search.</li></ol>
<div class="video"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DbRocGg6kbw" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
<p class="p">Personalize NeedIt List</p>
</div>
<p> </p>]]></content>
